<content type="str">A prominent Melbourne Muslim restaurateur has labelled US President Donald Trump&apos;s 90-day visa ban on residents from seven Muslim-majority nations as amounting to tyranny and bigotry. 

Hana Assafiri​ described the move as a &quot;war&quot; against Muslims, and that human rights were being scaled back, which was &quot;scary&quot;. 

